{
  "docTitle": "立即报价上传 | 敏捷智造",
  "bodyClasses": [
    "quote-guest-page"
  ],
  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"guest-quote-hero is-upload-layout\" id=\"quote-upload\">\n<div class=\"container guest-entry-bar\">\n<div aria-label=\"解决方案入口\" class=\"guest-mode-switch\">\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option is-active\" data-mode-option=\"quickQuote\" type=\"button\">快速报价</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"smartQuote\" type=\"button\">智能报价</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"rapidPrototype\" type=\"button\">快速原型</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"dfm\" type=\"button\">DFM检查</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"imageTo3d\" type=\"button\">图生3D模型</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"textTo3d\" type=\"button\">文生3D模型</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"formatConvert\" type=\"button\">3D格式转换</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"threeToTwo\" type=\"button\">3D转2D工程图</button>\n<button class=\"guest-mode-option\" data-mode-option=\"bubble\" type=\"button\">2D气泡图标注</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container guest-quote-layout\">\n<div class=\"guest-quote-copy\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\" data-mode-kicker=\"\">INSTANT QUOTE</span>\n<h1 data-mode-title=\"\">上传模型，快速获取制造报价</h1>\n<p data-mode-description=\"\">提交 3D 模型、2D 图纸或 PDF 资料后，我们会围绕材料、工艺、数量、交期和表面处理要求进行报价评估，帮助您更快判断项目成本与制造路径。</p>\n<div aria-label=\"报价入口优势\" class=\"guest-quote-points\">\n<span data-mode-point=\"0\">多格式上传</span>\n<span data-mode-point=\"1\">DFM 初步评估</span>\n<span data-mode-point=\"2\">人工报价可选</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guest-upload-card is-upload-mode\" id=\"guest-panel\">\n<div class=\"guest-upload-head\">\n<div>\n<h2 data-card-title=\"\">上传报价文件</h2>\n<p data-card-description=\"\">支持单个零件或多个工程文件，模型与图纸可一起提交。</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"guest-upload-badge\" data-card-badge=\"\">快速报价入口</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guest-drop-zone\" id=\"drop-zone\">\n<div>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"guest-upload-icon\">\n<svg fill=\"none\" role=\"img\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M12 15V4m0 0 4 4m-4-4-4 4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path>\n<path d=\"M5 14v3.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 7.5 20h9a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5-2.5V14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<h3 data-drop-title=\"\">拖拽文件到这里，或点击选择文件</h3>\n<p data-drop-detail=\"\">支持 .STEP、.STP、.STL、.IGES、.OBJ、.DWG、.DXF、.PDF，单文件建议不超过 100MB。</p>\n<button class=\"guest-file-button\" data-file-button=\"\" type=\"button\">浏览文件</button>\n<input accept=\".step,.stp,.stl,.iges,.igs,.obj,.dwg,.dxf,.pdf\" hidden=\"\" id=\"file-input\" multiple=\"\" type=\"file\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guest-lite-chat\">\n<div class=\"guest-chat-quota\">\n<div>\n<strong>游客对话</strong>\n<span data-quota-copy=\"\">游客模式剩余 3 次轻量对话</span>\n</div>\n<span class=\"guest-quota-pill\" data-quota-pill=\"\">0 / 3</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guest-chat-board\" data-chat-board=\"\">\n<div class=\"guest-chat-bubble\" data-chat-welcome=\"\">可以先描述零件、图片或模型目标，我会帮你整理下一步需要进入的工作台。</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guest-chat-message\" data-chat-answer=\"\"><strong>AgileMakeAI：</strong>可以先上传资料，也可以用一句话补充材料、数量、交期或应用场景。</div>\n<div class=\"guest-composer\">\n<button aria-label=\"上传附件\" class=\"guest-icon-action\" id=\"chat-upload-trigger\" type=\"button\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M12 5v14M5 12h14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.9\"></path>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<textarea class=\"guest-need-input\" id=\"guest-need-input\" maxlength=\"240\" placeholder=\"描述需求、材料、数量、交期或模型生成目标...\"></textarea>\n<button aria-label=\"发送\" class=\"guest-primary-action guest-send-action\" id=\"send-guest-message\" type=\"button\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M5 12h13m0 0-5-5m5 5-5 5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path>\n</svg>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"guest-chat-actions\">\n<div class=\"guest-quick-chips\">\n<button class=\"guest-quick-chip\" data-quick-chip=\"材料：铝合金 6061-T6；数量：50 件；交期：10 天。\" type=\"button\">报价参数</button>\n<button class=\"guest-quick-chip\" data-quick-chip=\"需要先检查结构可制造性，并标出加工风险。\" type=\"button\">DFM 风险</button>\n<button class=\"guest-quick-chip\" data-quick-chip=\"希望生成可进一步评估的 3D 模型方向。\" type=\"button\">模型生成</button>\n</div>\n<button class=\"guest-primary-action\" id=\"continue-workbench\" type=\"button\">进入工作台</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"guest-status hidden\" id=\"status-area\">\n<div>\n<strong data-status-title=\"\">文件已接收</strong>\n<span data-status-detail=\"\">下一步可继续补充报价所需的材料、数量和交期信息。</span>\n</div>\n<span data-status-percent=\"\">已暂存</span>\n</div>\n<div aria-label=\"报价方式选择\" class=\"quote-choice-strip\">\n<div class=\"quote-choice-copy\">\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"quote-choice-icon\">\n<svg fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<path d=\"M12 3 5 6v5c0 4.5 2.8 8.1 7 10 4.2-1.9 7-5.5 7-10V6l-7-3Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"></path>\n<path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.7\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<span data-choice-copy=\"\">工程资料仅用于报价评估；复杂项目、批量采购或无法上传模型时，可直接发起人工报价。</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"quote-choice-actions\">\n<a data-choice-primary=\"\" href=\"/solutions/instant-quoting\">查看样例</a>\n<a data-choice-secondary=\"\" href=\"/about#contact\">人工报价 / RFQ</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section aria-label=\"报价工作流\" class=\"container quote-workflow-section\">\n<div class=\"quote-workflow-head\">\n<h2 data-workflow-title=\"\">报价流程介绍</h2>\n<p data-workflow-description=\"\">为了让您在提交资料前更清楚后续步骤，我们将从文件上传到报价确认的关键环节整理如下，便于提前准备材料、数量、交期和质量要求。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"quote-workflow-track\">\n<article class=\"quote-workflow-step\"><b>01</b><h3 data-workflow-step-title=\"0\">上传零件资料</h3><p data-workflow-step-copy=\"0\">提交 3D 模型、2D 图纸、PDF 说明或关键加工要求。</p></article>\n<article class=\"quote-workflow-step\"><b>02</b><h3 data-workflow-step-title=\"1\">补充报价参数</h3><p data-workflow-step-copy=\"1\">确认材料、数量、表面处理、公差重点和目标交期。</p></article>\n<article class=\"quote-workflow-step\"><b>03</b><h3 data-workflow-step-title=\"2\">工程评估报价</h3><p data-workflow-step-copy=\"2\">进行 DFM 检查、工艺路径判断、成本拆分和风险提示。</p></article>\n<article class=\"quote-workflow-step\"><b>04</b><h3 data-workflow-step-title=\"3\">确认订单交付</h3><p data-workflow-step-copy=\"3\">确认报价后进入生产排期、质检跟踪与交付协同。</p></article>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
}
